videos.description: Tanner Morgan hits Tyler Johnson on a slant route for an 18-yard touchdown to extend Minnesota's lead to 21-9.
videos.headline: Morgan connects with Johnson for 18-yard TD

videos.description: Indiana's Donovan Hale gets a step on the defender and hauls in a 43-yard touchdown pass from Peyton Ramsey.
videos.headline: Ramsey launches a 43-yard TD to Hale

videos.description: Indiana QB Peyton Ramsey connects with Ty Fryfogle for a 37-yard touchdown to cut Minnesota's lead to 31-23 with 10:04 left in the game.
videos.headline: Ramsey threads the needle for a 37-yard TD

videos.description: Peyton Ramsey runs for 30 yards to set up a 1st-and-goal followed by a Stevie Scott TD. Indiana would go for 2 to tie the game at 31-31.
videos.headline: Ramsey's big run sets up Scott's 3-yard TD
